data.description: LAKE FRONT- Welcome to this beautiful 5-bedroom, 4-bathroom two-story lake front home NO FLOOD ZONE, meaning lender does not require flood insurance. This home is located in the community of the River Club and has an open floor plan that seamlessly blends comfort and functionality. As you step through the front door, you're greeted by the two-story foyer. To the left is the formal dining room or this area can be used as a flex space. To the right is a downstairs bathroom and bedroom. Continue down the hall to the heart of the home an open concept living area that effortlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen. The living room is a cozy yet spacious retreat, perfect for both intimate family evenings and entertaining guests. The kitchen is a chef's dream with granite countertops, ample cabinetry that elegantly combines form and function, stainless steel appliances and a convection oven. The spacious center island/breakfast bar is a natural gathering spot, ideal for casual meals or hosting culinary experiments with friends and family. Between the living room and the kitchen is a smaller dining area perfect for a more informal dinette. Step out the French doors to the outdoor living space, an extension of the indoor living area, this spacious screened in patio is perfect for lounging and taking in the lake view or hosting summer barbecues.  Ascending the staircase to the second level, you'll find a loft to use to your liking, perfect for a game room, family room or cozy sitting area. The Primary Bedroom is set off from the loft for privacy and leads to a stunning suite featuring a large walk-in closet and on-suite bathroom with dual sinks and an oversized walk-in shower. There are three additional well-appointed bedrooms. One of them having it's own bathroom. These rooms can effortlessly transform to suit your needs, whether you're accommodating a growing family or creating personalized spaces for work, hobbies, or guests. Also located upstairs is an indoor laundry room an another bathroom with dual sinks. This home offers it all and is waiting for a family to move in and make it their own.  The River Club community is a gated community with 3 ponds and offers a fitness center, community pool, cable TV & internet service, grounds/pool maintenance and lawn irrigation. MINUTES to US 41 & I75 for easy access to downtown Punta Gorda, local shopping & boutiques, fine & casual dining, LIVE entertainment and the Punta Gorda Airport.
